@baseUrl = http://localhost:5188
@accept = application/json

### ========================================
### Segments
### ========================================

### Get all catalog segments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/segments?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### Get categories by segment (root categories with hierarchy)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/segments/1/categories?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### ========================================
### Categories
### ========================================

### Get all root level categories (with hierarchy and segment info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### Get category by ID (with full hierarchy and segment info)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### Get products by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1/products?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### ========================================
### Products
### ========================================

###

### Get product with many parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### Get related products for a product (based on shared categories)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1/related?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### ========================================
### Recommendations (GDS-powered similarity)
### ========================================

### Get recommendations for a product
# Note: Run deploy/scripts/compute-similarity.cypher first
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations?productId=1&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### Get recommendations for product 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations?productId=2&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### Get recommendations page 2 (for large result sets)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/recommendations?productId=1&page=2&pageSize=10
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### ========================================
### Search (Global autocomplete)
### ========================================

### Search for products, categories, and brands
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?q=phone&limit=5
Accept: {{accept}}

###

### Search with different term
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?q=sport&limit=10
Accept: {{accept}}

###
